components.description: A group of buttons within a grid layout, having a single callback/event. Updated to inherit from component container rather than base widget.
A group of checkboxes in list format (scrollable if needed) Inherits from matlab ui componentController.
A color selection control with browse button. Updated to inherit from ComponentContainer rather than BaseWidget.
A date and time selection control. Update to inherit from ComponentContainer.
A file/folder selection control with browse button. Updated to inherit from ComponentContainer.

A list with configurable buttons alongside. Use the buttons to add, remove, or rearrange the displayed items from a known set. Custom buttons may also be added. Derives from UI component container instead of BaseWidget class.

A pair of list controls with configurable buttons alongside. Use the buttons to add items from the left to the right and back or to rearrange the selected items. Custom buttons may also be added. Inherits from matlab.ui.ComponentContainer
A password entry field where the text is hidden as dots. Derives from ui.componentcontainer.ComponentContainer
A progress bar that can optionally display time remaining, status message, and cancel button. It can also be made indeterminate to show "busy" status. Inherits from UI Component Container + Mixins.

A group of sliders paired with checkboxes to enable or disable the slider. (Example usage: adjusting opacity of layers in 2D or 3D graphics.) Added Background Colorability. Inherits from superclass matlab.ui.componentcontainer.ComponentContainer.
A slider and spinner combination for editing and adjusting a scalar numeric value. Inherits from matlab.ui.componentcontainer.
A vertical list of tasks with icons to show their status, such as incomplete, complete, error, etc. Inherits from matab.ui.componentcontainer.

A configurable toolbar, similar to the MATLAB toolstrip. Adding sections and controls must be done programmatically. For more information, see WidgetExamples.mlx. Now inherits from matlab.ui.componentcontainer.
